      "message": "I guess this is related to an earlier change in the series, but I don\u0027t get how this can be \"always\". When the client gives us a MSAA buffer, we don\u0027t want to discard it, right? Also, what if they pass a sample count to say MakeRenderTarget, don\u0027t we want that to work the same as it does now?",
